{"id": "srw1665702550375", "title": "Main Development Object", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "Development Object and Property Reference", "Development Objects Reference", "Main Development Object"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/srw1665702550375.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">Main Development Object</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous:   Code Container \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous:   Code Container \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:   Reference Development Object \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:   Reference Development Object \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fct1665702713420.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/srw1665702550375.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/srw1665702550375.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/srw1665702550375.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615947\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615947\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104srw1665702550375.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/srw1665702550375.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/srw1665702550375.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"srw1665702550375\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Main Development Object\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"srw1665702550375__main_development_object_309212\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Main Development Object is a Development Object that has no parent object, is maintained using a dedicated editor, and can be saved and exported as a single unit, with all its children.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"srw1665702550375__p_d94538e1_d94539e1_d94540e1\">It provides the starting point for creating and editing a collection of development objects that together define a logical unit such as a modeled entity, component, or library.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"srw1665702550375__p_d94541e1_d94542e1_d94543e1\">For example, a <dfn class=\"term\">Component</dfn> is a Main Development Object that has properties and code containers, and contains specific types of development objects, such as component entities, component fields, labels, and their child objects, properties, and code containers.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"srw1665702550375__topic_d62962e1_d62963e1_d62964e1_d62965e1_d62966e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d910827e62\">\n                     \n Characteristics\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__2\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"srw1665702550375__fig_w1326ab1b5b7b3b3b7b1b3b1b1_w1327ab1b5b7b3b3b7b1b3b1_w1328ab1b5b7b3b3b7b1b3_w1329ab1b5b7b3b3b7b1_w1330ab1b5b7b3b3b7_w1331ab1b5b7b3b3_w1332ab1b5b7b3_w1333ab1b5b7_w1334ab1b5_w1335ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"srw1665702550375__image_egz_kxs_4wb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/main_udo.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"quf1665702550125.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/quf1665702550125.html\" title=\"An Application Shell is a Main Development Object that defines the main executable component of an application (Windows or character-based) or application server.\">Application Shell</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifc1665702608950.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifc1665702608950.html\" title=\"A Component is a Main Development Object that defines an executable part of an application. It defines the data structure used to access data, the layout (if applicable) used to present it, and the actions used to modify, validate, and store data.\">Component</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"scm1665702714238.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scm1665702714238.html\" title=\"A Library is a Main Development Object that holds a collection of objects of the same type that can be accessed or reused by other objects, either during development or at runtime.\">Library</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tza1665702561698.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tza1665702561698.html\" title=\"A Modeled Entity is an Entity that defines a logical data aggregation at an abstract level. It is used to model the default properties and code of an entity, so that the Entity can be referenced and inherited by derived entities in components.\">Modeled Entity</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qvi1665702713514.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qvi1665702713514.html\" title=\"A Project is a Main Development Object that defines the contents of an application or part of an application, and is used to control the build process. It is the starting point for all development and contains Reference Development Objects that refer to Main Development Objects.\">Project</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"unm1665702654361.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/unm1665702654361.html\" title=\"A DTD is a Main Development Object that represents a Document Type Definition that defines element declarations and a default mapping between the XML elements and Component Entities and Fields.\">DTD</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ird1665702714456.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ird1665702714456.html\" title=\"A Signature is a Development Object that describes the remote interface of a component, or modeled entity operation. Signatures for Uniface components and modeled entity operations are automatically generated, but signatures for non-Uniface components that Uniface can call at runtime, must be explicitly defined.\">Signature</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Depends on the specialized object</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"srw1665702550375__table_d10454e1_d10455e1_d10456e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"srw1665702550375__topic_d62967e1_d62968e1_d62969e1_d62970e1_d62971e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d910827e321\"> Specialization </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"srw1665702550375__p_d94550e1_d94551e1_d94552e1\">Main Development Object is an abstract, complex data\n            type that specializes Development Object in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"srw1665702550375__li_d36800e1_d36801e1_d36802e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"srw1665702550375__p_d94553e1_d94554e1_d94555e1\">It has no parent object</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"srw1665702550375__li_d36803e1_d36804e1_d36805e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"srw1665702550375__p_d94556e1_d94557e1_d94558e1\">It cannot contain other Main development\n                  objects</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"srw1665702550375__li_d36806e1_d36807e1_d36808e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"srw1665702550375__p_d94559e1_d94560e1_d94561e1\">It has an associated editor that is used to\n                  maintain it and its child development objects, properties, and code</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"srw1665702550375__li_d36809e1_d36810e1_d36811e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"srw1665702550375__p_d94562e1_d94563e1_d94564e1\">It can be saved, with all its children, to the\n                  work area as a single file</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"srw1665702550375__li_d36812e1_d36813e1_d36814e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"srw1665702550375__p_d94565e1_d94566e1_d94567e1\">It can be loaded from the work area, discarding\n                  the existing Main object in the repository (if it already exists)</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615947\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615947\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Main Development Object Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Main Development Object A Main Development Object is a Development Object that has no parent object, is maintained using a dedicated editor, and can be saved and exported as a single unit, with all its children. It provides the starting point for creating and editing a collection of development objects that together define a logical unit such as a modeled entity, component, or library. For example, a Component is a Main Development Object that has properties and code containers, and contains specific types of development objects, such as component entities, component fields, labels, and their child objects, properties, and code containers. Characteristics Characteristics Icon Object type code: — Main Development Object? Yes Part of: — Contains: Development Object , Property , Code Container Generalization: Development Object Specializations: Application Shell , Component , Library , Modeled Entity , Project , DTD , Signature Compilation output: Depends on the specialized object URI format: — Specialization Main Development Object is an abstract, complex data type that specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has no parent object It cannot contain other Main development objects It has an associated editor that is used to maintain it and its child development objects, properties, and code It can be saved, with all its children, to the work area as a single file It can be loaded from the work area, discarding the existing Main object in the repository (if it already exists) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}